MERIDIAN ECOMMERCE EMAIL FLOW TEMPLATES

The real archive contains eight complete email flows, each with full copy (subject lines, preheaders, body, CTAs), segmentation rules, trigger timing, and a README explaining the revenue model behind each flow. Flows included: 5-email welcome series, 3-email abandoned cart, 2-email browse abandonment, 4-email post-purchase nurture, 3-email winback for lapsed customers, 1-email replenishment for consumables, 3-email VIP/loyalty tier, and 2-email review-and-UGC request.

Every flow is provided as importable Klaviyo and Mailchimp exports plus a platform-agnostic Markdown version so you can port the copy to any ESP. Supporting documents include a deliverability checklist (SPF, DKIM, DMARC, warm-up cadence), a revenue attribution model (flow-level and SKU-level), and an A/B testing framework for subject lines and send times.

Designed for Shopify, WooCommerce and Magento stores generating anywhere from £50k to £50M+ annual revenue. Copy tone is deliberately brand-agnostic and can be adapted for DTC fashion, beauty, home, food & beverage, or B2B ecommerce with minimal rewriting.
